1 - Create a new Content Type (CT) in Contentstack for the homepage block.
2 - Sync the TypeScript types (tsgen) and create a sample entry for this CT.
3 - Create a new component in the codebase for this block.
4 - Design and style the component as required.
5 - Integrate the component where it needs to be rendered on the homepage.
6 - If it represents a full page, define the route/path and create the corresponding structure in the Next.js app directory.
7 - Test the implementation across different devices and screen sizes.

